social_posts.post_text: Are you looking for something to do this weekend? You should come see The Air and Sea Show this Memorial Day Weekend! Known as “The Greatest Show Above the Earth”, it showcases people from all six branches of the United States Military, as well as police, firefighters, and first responder agencies. All on the beautiful shores of Miami Beach, this event will feature the Cigarette offshore powerboat racing exhibition, extreme water sports, the FPL Display Village, and more. It really is an event you can’t miss! #miami #miamibeach #memorialdayweekend #realestate #events #florida #lifestyle #livinglife
